<p><a name="Sephardic" id="Sephardic"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Cantillation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Sephardic">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Sephardic</span></h4>
<div class="center">
<div class="thumb tnone">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:582px;"><a href="/wiki/File:TAMI_MIKRA_MIZRAH.png" class="image" title="TAMI MIKRA MIZRAH.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/46/TAMI_MIKRA_MIZRAH.png/580px-TAMI_MIKRA_MIZRAH.png" width="580" height="246" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:TAMI_MIKRA_MIZRAH.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
